Delete a warn from a user.

## Usage

```sh
;delwarn <warn ID>
```

## Examples

```sh
# delete the warn with ID 'cjld2cjxh0000qzrmn831i7rn'
;delwarn cjld2cjxh0000qzrmn831i7rn
```
